statements.sql: select `id`, `title`, `excerpt`, `slug`, `published`, `image`, `viewed`, `is_video`, `read_time`, `excerpt` from `articles` where exists (select * from `categories` inner join `article_categories` on `categories`.`id` = `article_categories`.`category_id` where `articles`.`id` = `article_categories`.`article_id` and `is_published` = 1) and `published` = 1 order by `viewed` desc limit 5

select `categories`.`id`, `categories`.`name`, `categories`.`slug`, `article_categories`.`article_id` as `pivot_article_id`, `article_categories`.`category_id` as `pivot_category_id`, `article_categories`.`id` as `pivot_id` from `categories` inner join `article_categories` on `categories`.`id` = `article_categories`.`category_id` where `article_categories`.`article_id` in (6, 8, 9, 10, 15)
select * from `keywords` where `title` LIKE '%Linnéa Findeklee Kolumne%'

select `id`, `name`, `slug`, `is_published`, `is_video` from `categories` where `is_published` = 1 and `is_video` = 0 and `is_published` = 1 and `display_in_home_page` = 1 and exists (select * from `articles` inner join `article_categories` on `articles`.`id` = `article_categories`.`article_id` where `categories`.`id` = `article_categories`.`category_id` and `published` = 1) order by `position` asc

select `article_id`, `title`, `slug`, `published`, `viewed`, `image`, `featured`, `read_time`, `article_categories`.`category_id` as `pivot_category_id`, `article_categories`.`article_id` as `pivot_article_id` from `articles` inner join `article_categories` on `articles`.`id` = `article_categories`.`article_id` where `article_categories`.`category_id` in (4, 8) order by `article_id` desc

select `id`, `title`, `slug`, `published`, `image`, `description`, `is_video` from `articles` where exists (select * from `categories` inner join `article_categories` on `categories`.`id` = `article_categories`.`category_id` where `articles`.`id` = `article_categories`.`article_id` and `is_published` = 1) and `published` = 1 and `is_video` = 1 order by `created_at` desc limit 3
select * from `ad_spaces` where `name` = 'home_page_full_width_ad' and `published` = 1 order by `created_at` desc limit 1
select * from `ad_spaces` where `name` = 'home_page_popular_article_section_ad' and `published` = 1 order by `created_at` desc limit 1
select * from `ad_spaces` where `name` = 'home_page_category_section_full_width_ad' and `published` = 1 order by `created_at` desc limit 1
